videos.description: Juwan Gary gets fired up after he goes up and through contact to get the and-1 layup on the break.

videos.description: Chharles Bediako goes up to get the pass from Jahvon Quinerly and rises up to stuff down the easy two-handed jam.

videos.headline: Jahvon Quinerly finds Charles Bediako for a dunk

videos.description: Jahvon Quinerly gets the defensive rebound, races down the court and rises up to switches hands midair to score a fast-break layup for Alabama.

videos.description: Jaden Shackelford knocks down an and-1 3-pointer then follows it up with another deep three as Alabama battles Houston late in the second half.

videos.description: JD Davison elevates to grab the miss and smashes down a two-handed dunk for Alabama.

videos.headline: JD Davison elevates to flush 2nd-chance dunk for Bama

videos.description: JD Davison throws down a big-time putback dunk, then comes up with a big defensive play on the other end to help seal an 83-82 win for Alabama over Houston.
